summary: AN ORDINANCE authorizing an amendment to the agreement authorized by Ordinance 99257 with the State of Washington Interagency Committee for Outdoor Recreation for a grant to aid in acquisition of certain land as permanent open space for park and recreation purposes (Project No. IAC \#4KNG-70-045A - Fauntleroy park) to reduce the total amount of such grant in aid and the acreage to be acquired.
